220
00:17:19,724 --> 00:17:21,524
<font color="yellow">Kakek, minum tehnya.</font>

221
00:17:25,324 --> 00:17:27,654
<font color="yellow">- Ayah, minum juga.
- Baiklah.</font>

222
00:17:34,994 --> 00:17:37,964
<font color="yellow">Teh jujube aromanya luar biasa.</font>

223
00:17:37,984 --> 00:17:40,544
<font color="yellow">Iya. Itu baik dan hangat.</font>

224
00:17:41,474 --> 00:17:43,754
<font color="yellow">Aku merebus jujubes kering untuk waktu yang lama.</font>

225
00:17:44,364 --> 00:17:47,784
<font color="yellow">Cuacanya semakin dingin, jadi tingkat kekebalan
tubuhmu tidak oleh turun.</font>

226
00:17:48,234 --> 00:17:52,044
<font color="yellow">Kau bahkan merawat kesehatanku sekarang.</font>

227
00:17:52,614 --> 00:17:54,394
<font color="yellow">Aku sangat bahagia.</font>

228
00:17:56,294 --> 00:18:00,584
<font color="yellow">Saat cuaca semakin dingin,
