284
00:21:12,384 --> 00:21:14,574
<font color="yellow">Sudah cukup. Duduk.</font>

285
00:21:14,814 --> 00:21:15,944
<font color="yellow">Aku belum selesai.</font>

286
00:21:18,544 --> 00:21:20,544
<font color="yellow">Berikan kakimu kepadaku.</font>

287
00:21:22,664 --> 00:21:24,174
<font color="yellow">Lihatlah bagaimana melepuhnya kakimu.</font>

288
00:21:25,924 --> 00:21:29,404
<font color="yellow">Itu semua sia-sia.</font>

289
00:21:31,624 --> 00:21:32,944
<font color="yellow">Apa yang kau bicarakan?</font>

290
00:21:33,374 --> 00:21:34,414
<font color="yellow">Sayang...</font>

291
00:21:35,624 --> 00:21:36,734
<font color="yellow">aku lelah.</font>

292
00:21:37,194 --> 00:21:38,514
<font color="yellow">Kalau begitu pergi tidur.</font>

293
00:21:39,574 --> 00:21:43,364
<font color="yellow">Sayang, beri aku pijatan kaki.</font>

294
00:21:44,344 --> 00:21:45,934
<font color="yellow">Masukan air ke dalam bak.</font>

295
00:21:48,364 --> 00:21:50,224
<font color="yellow">Apa kau salah makan sesuatu ?</font>

296
00:21:51,034 --> 00:21:52,034
<font color="yellow">Sayang...</font>

297
00:21:53,264 --> 00:22:01,154
<font color="yellow">kakiku benar-benar lelah hari ini.</font>

298
00:22:02,274 --> 00:22:04,624
<font color="yellow">Singkirkan kaki babi raksasa itu!</font>

299
00:22:05,174 --> 00:22:07,064
<font color="yellow">Ya ampun.</font>

300
00:22:08,884 --> 00:22:10,214
<font color="yellow">Apa? Kaki babi?</font>

301
00:22:10,544 --> 00:22:12,624
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana bisa aku menyebutnya suamiku?</font>

302
00:22:13,524 --> 00:22:15,944
<font color="yellow">Mereka mengatakan wanita yang tidak memiliki
