<font color="yellow">Sampai jumpa, kakek!</font>

328
00:23:58,524 --> 00:23:59,524
<font color="yellow">Sampai jumpa.</font>

329
00:24:01,044 --> 00:24:02,474
<font color="yellow">Aku akan kembali.</font>

330
00:24:12,034 --> 00:24:15,104
<font color="yellow">Pelayan, apa yang sedang kau lakukan?</font>

331
00:24:15,714 --> 00:24:19,264
<font color="yellow">Apa maksudmu? Kenapa bersikap seperti ini lagi?</font>

332
